flowchart TB
    A[Beam at start of scanline] --> B[CPU has 76 cycles]
    B --> C[Write player position registers]
    C --> D[Update playfield bits for this line]
    D --> E[Set sprite graphics for this line]
    E --> F[WSYNC: halt CPU until next line]
    F --> G[Beam at start of next scanline]
    G --> B

    style C fill:#cfe8d4,stroke:#2a7a3a,color:#000
    style F fill:#f7d6cf,stroke:#a23a2a,color:#000
